title: NFL ATL: Brandon Marshall interview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Brandon Marshall interview
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- welcome Chicago Bears wide receiver Brandon Marshall to the studio, chat playoffs with NFL Media's Andrew Siciliano and get you caught up to date on the latest headlines from around the league.  Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
